While on the topic of Rd macro arguments, it seems that  if a multiline argument is supplied, the lines after the first are silently ignored:

f <- tempfile()
mac6 <- "\\newcommand{\\mac6}{mac6: #1}"

cat(mac6, "\\mac6{2*3
2+2
sin(pi)
}\n", file = f)
rd <- tools::parse_Rd(f)

> rd
 mac6: 2*3

---

Georgi Boshnakov


